title: Cell 1
treatment_protocol_ch1: Cells were incubated in BioSpherix hypoxia chamber under hypoxic conditions (1% O2) or in a Thermo Scientific cell culture incubator under “normoxic” conditions (20% O2), in all cases at 37C and 5% CO2.
growth_protocol_ch1: Cells were cultured in RPMI + 1X Pen/Strep, 10% exosome-free FBS (prepared through ultracentrifugation of FBS - 100,000xg for 6h).
extract_protocol_ch1: RNA was extracted using the Qiagen miRNEasy kit
label_protocol_ch1: 130ng RNA was labeled using the Affymetrix HSR miRNA Flash Tag Biotin kit
hyb_protocol: 130ng labeled RNA was hybridized for 18 hr at 48C on GeneChip miRNA 3.0 Arrays. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 450
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix GeneChip Scanner 3000 7G
data_processing: The data were analyzed with Partek Genomcis Suite(v.6.6) using the RMA normalization method
contact_address: 3181 SW Sam Jackson Park Rd, Mail Code #L581
